00:10:18.200 --> 00:10:18.799
Manatiling alerto.

00:10:18.860 --> 00:10:19.680
Maghiwa-hiwalay na kayo at maghanap!

00:10:40.879 --> 00:10:41.759
Pangalawang Sugo Gao,

00:10:41.919 --> 00:10:43.399
